"title": "7105: believers",
"media_type": "Text",
"index_reference": "7105",
"language": "eng",
"review_level": "None",
"content": "<p>Those who have faith in God. After Pentecost, the term came to be used specifically to refer to Christians, that is, to those who believe and trust in God, as he has made himself known through Jesus Christ. The NT stresses that Jesus Christ brings the faith of OT believers to perfection and to its proper fulfilment.</p>\n<h2>Believers as those who have faith in God</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Kgs18:3-1Kgs18:4\">1KI 18:3–18:4</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/John4:39-John4:42\">JHN 4:39–4:42</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts16:15\">ACT 16:15</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jas2:1\">JAS 2:1</a></p>\n<h2>OT believers looked forward to the NT faith</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Heb11:13\">HEB 11:13</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Heb11:39\">HEB 11:39</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Pet1:10-1Pet1:12\">1PE 1:10–1:12</a></p>\n<h2>The church is referred to as the believers</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts5:12\">ACT 5:12</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts1:15\">ACT 1:15</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts2:44\">ACT 2:44</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts4:32\">ACT 4:32</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts9:41\">ACT 9:41</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Tim4:12\">1TI 4:12</a></p>\n<h2>In the early church a distinction was sometimes made between Jewish and Gentile believers</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts15:23\">ACT 15:23</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts10:45\">ACT 10:45</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts11:1-Acts11:3\">ACT 11:1–11:3</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts15:5\">ACT 15:5</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts21:20-Acts21:25\">ACT 21:20–21:25</a></p>\n<h2>The term believer is synonymous with Christian</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Cor7:12-1Cor7:13\">1CO 7:12–7:13</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts15:2\">ACT 15:2</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts16:1\">ACT 16:1</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Cor6:5\">1CO 6:5</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Cor14:22\">1CO 14:22</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Cor6:14-2Cor6:15\">2CO 6:14–6:15</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Thess1:7\">1TH 1:7</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Tim5:16\">1TI 5:16</a></p>\n<h2>Believers are members of God's family</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gal6:10\">GAL 6:10</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Tim6:2\">1TI 6:2</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Pet2:17\">1PE 2:17</a></p>",
